column1: # AP name is mandatory. The name can only contain between 2 and 32 characters. Only the following characters are allowed: 'a-z', 'A-Z', '0-9', space and other special characters (!"#$%'()*+,-./:;<=>?@[]^_{|}~) except &,` or $(
# AP Group - must match an existing AP group
# Latitude - between -90 and 90, and contains a maximum of 6-digit decimal
# Longitude - between -180 and 180, and contains a maximum of 6-digit decimal
